# Chargezio API — REST Client test file
# Install VS Code extension: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
# Click "Send Request" above any ### block to run it.
#
# FLOW:
#   1. Health check
#   2. Send OTP → response has { expiresAt } (use for countdown timer)
#   3. Verify OTP → paste token below
#   4. Top up wallet → ₹500
#   5. Browse nearby stations → grab a stationId + chargerId
#   6. Start session → grab sessionId
#   7. Poll GET session every few seconds to see live data
#   8. Stop session → wallet deducted, transaction created

@base = http://localhost:5000
@phone = +919876543210

# ─── paste JWT here after verify-otp ────────────────────────────────────────
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

# ─── paste IDs from responses ────────────────────────────────────────────────
@vehicleId       = PASTE_VEHICLE_ID_HERE
@stationId       = PASTE_STATION_ID_HERE
@sessionId       = PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE
@razorpayOrderId = PASTE_ORDER_ID_FROM_INITIATE


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HEALTH
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Health check
GET {{base}}/health


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AUTH
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 2. Send OTP  →  { expiresAt } for countdown timer
POST {{base}}/api/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

###

### 3. Verify OTP  →  paste { token } into @token above
POST {{base}}/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{phone}}",
  "otp": "ENTER_6_DIGIT_OTP"
}

###

### 4. Logout
POST {{base}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PROFILE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 5. Get full profile + vehicles
GET {{base}}/api/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Create profile  (one-time; 409 if already done)
POST {{base}}/api/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pratyaksh Pandey",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "city": "Bengaluru",
  "gender": "male",
  "preferredConnector": "CCS2",
  "preferredSpeed": "DC Fast",
  "vehicle": {
    "brand": "Tata",
    "model": "Nexon EV",
    "type": "BEV",
    "batteryKWh": 40.5,
    "rangeKm": 465,
    "connector": "CCS2",
    "plateNumber": "KA01AB1234"
  }
}

###

### 7. Update profile
PUT {{base}}/api/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "preferredSpeed": "Ultra Fast"
}

###

### 8. Stats  (real session aggregation)
GET {{base}}/api/profile/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Delete account  (soft-delete — uncomment only if you mean it)
# DELETE {{base}}/api/profile
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VEHICLES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 10. List vehicles
GET {{base}}/api/profile/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. Add a second vehicle
POST {{base}}/api/profile/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "MG",
  "model": "ZS EV",
  "type": "BEV",
  "batteryKWh": 50.3,
  "rangeKm": 461,
  "connector": "CCS2",
  "plateNumber": "KA05CD5678"
}

###

### 12. Update vehicle
PUT {{base}}/api/profile/vehicles/{{vehicleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rangeKm": 480,
  "plateNumber": "KA01ZZ9999"
}

###

### 13. Set as primary
PATCH {{base}}/api/profile/vehicles/{{vehicleId}}/primary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 14. Delete vehicle
DELETE {{base}}/api/profile/vehicles/{{vehicleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WALLET
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 15. Get wallet balance + last 10 transactions
GET {{base}}/api/wallet
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 16. Initiate top-up  →  creates Razorpay order; paste orderId into @razorpayOrderId above
POST {{base}}/api/wallet/topup/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500
}

###

### 16b. Verify top-up  →  call after Razorpay checkout succeeds; credits wallet
# razorpaySignature comes from the Razorpay checkout callback
POST {{base}}/api/wallet/topup/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "razorpayOrderId":   "{{razorpayOrderId}}",
  "razorpayPaymentId": "pay_PASTE_PAYMENT_ID",
  "razorpaySignature": "PASTE_SIGNATURE_FROM_CHECKOUT"
}

###

### 17. Full transaction history  (paginated)
GET {{base}}/api/wallet/transactions?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CHARGING STATIONS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 18. Nearby stations  →  paste a stationId + chargerId into vars above
# Coordinates: Bellandur, Bengaluru
GET {{base}}/api/stations/nearby?lat=12.9352&lng=77.6245&radius=5000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 19. Nearby — filter by connector + type
GET {{base}}/api/stations/nearby?lat=12.9352&lng=77.6245&radius=10000&connector=CCS2&type=DC Fast
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 20. Station detail
GET {{base}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CHARGING SESSIONS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 21. Start charging session
# Prerequisites: wallet ≥ ₹50, charger must be 'available'
POST {{base}}/api/sessions/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stationId": "{{stationId}}",
  "chargerId": "CO-EB-0012",
  "targetSocPercent": 80,
  "startSocPercent": 22
}

###

### 22. Live session data  (poll every ~5s while session is active)
# Returns { live: { currentSocPercent, currentPowerKw, timeElapsed, energyDeliveredKwh,
#                   estimatedCostRs, estimatedRangeKm, fuelSavingsRs }, connectorStatus }
GET {{base}}/api/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 23. Stop charging  →  finalizes cost, deducts wallet, creates transaction
PATCH {{base}}/api/sessions/{{sessionId}}/stop
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 24. Session history (Trips tab)
GET {{base}}/api/sessions?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 25. Session history — completed only
GET {{base}}/api/sessions?status=completed&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
